{"type": "article", "id": 10005, "title": "“Tray Typer” 肯德基键盘", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-26T07:24:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235408jrhdZBfODymuEXwW.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t肯德基为了解决吃炸鸡的时候手上沾满油污而无法打字的问题，推出了这一款叫做 “Tray Typer” 的键盘。这是一个可充电的超薄蓝牙键盘，会随着肯德基的盘子连同食物一个端给你，通过蓝牙与附近的智能手机连接在一起，就可以愉快地一边吃炸鸡薯条，一边和朋友聊天了。实在是“孤独者的通行证”呢。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235407BwfqCUylkp0jTzRQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55378973\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235407AYMSEhig8PTo3v0L.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55623472\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523540863DQMaIusqrxLR5V.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}